b'Master of Science in Medical Biotechnology Program'
b'Master of Science in Medical Biotechnology Program'
b'tlowery1'
b'The Master of Science in Medical Biotechnology Program concentrates on biological processes, technologies and skill sets used in the research and development of pharmaceutical products, vaccines and devices for the medical industry, preparing students for a wide variety of research areas and career opportunities.'
b'\xe2\x80\x9cThe MBT Program at UIC is a rich learning culture which strives to bring the best out of every student. There is freedom to pursue our line of interests carving into our future paths. My experience being a part of the MBT family has molded me towards becoming a skilled biotech professional. I am very grateful to the staff and faculty for their continued support and guidance in shaping my career. I am proud to be an alumnus of the MBT family!\xe2\x80\x9d \xe2\x80\x94 Pooja Narendra, Senior Research Associate, Intellia Therapeutics, Inc.'
b'Research Areas:'
b'Drug Discovery & Development \xc2\xb7 Vaccines \xc2\xb7 Helminth Therapy \xc2\xb7 Cancer Research-Prostate, Lung, Skin & Breast \xc2\xb7 Stem Cells \xc2\xb7 Medical Devices/Implants \xc2\xb7 Immunotherapy \xc2\xb7 Metabolic Diseases-Diabetes, Atherosclerosis, Obesity'
